text: Basílio do Nascimento Martins (14 June 1950 – 30 October 2021) was the East Timorese Roman Catholic Bishop of Baucau from 2004 until his death. He was born in Suai, then Portuguese Timor. Nascimento became a priest in 1977. Nascimento died on 30 October 2021 at a hospital in Dili, East Timor from a heart attack, aged 71.Morreu Basílio do Nascimento, bispo da segunda maior cidade de Timor-Leste ==References== Category:1950 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Deaths from myocardial infarction Category:East Timorese people Category:Roman Catholic bishops
